				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You need to connect CLK and STROBE to two interrupt pins.<br />When you detect that STROBE pin is going high, value of A button outputted on DATA line.<br />Next you waits for rising edge on CLOCK pin. AFter first rising edge B button is outputted, then SELECET, START, UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT.<br />Because there is about 2-3 uS of delay between consecutive edges on CLK, you need to detect them and react for them fast. 16 MHz Crystal on arduino is needed.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

